The paper proposes a method for rice variety classification using hyperspectral imaging and deep convolutional neural network. This work involves computer vision (CV) techniques for image analysis and machine learning (ML) techniques for classification. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which fall under the sub-category cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper involves information retrieval (IR) techniques for feature extraction and classification, which falls under the sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also involves artificial intelligence (AI) techniques for classification, which falls under the sub-category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves multimedia (MM) techniques for image analysis, which falls under the sub-category cs.MM (Multimedia).
